<subSubSection id="40C4656BB824FFC249F1D754FA873E41" pageId="26" pageNumber="27" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="086136E0B824FFC249F1D754FA873E41" blockId="26.[151,1437,150,1149]" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">
<emphasis id="3AAAEAF2B824FFC249F1D754FE933E65" bold="true" box="[199,315,1087,1113]" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">Remarks.</emphasis>
Together with the three 
<typeStatus id="D7658842B824FFC24B67D754FD293E65" box="[593,641,1087,1113]" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">type</typeStatus>
specimens, Romeo Lumawig collected a specimen of 
<taxonomicName id="CFDE4D63B824FFC24DDFD754FA3D3E65" baseAuthorityName="Schaum" baseAuthorityYear="1862" box="[1257,1429,1087,1113]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Heptodonta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="26" pageNumber="27" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="melanopyga">
<emphasis id="3AAAEAF2B824FFC24DDFD754FA3D3E65" box="[1257,1429,1087,1113]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">H. melanopyga</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, showing the same specific colour pattern of 
<taxonomicName id="CFDE4D63B824FFC24BB0D708FCA03E40" box="[646,776,1123,1148]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Heptodonta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="26" pageNumber="27" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="wiesneri" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="3AAAEAF2B824FFC24BB0D708FCA03E40" box="[646,776,1123,1148]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">H. wiesneri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="3AAAEAF2B824FFC24A39D708FCC03E41" bold="true" box="[783,872,1123,1149]" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="21995789B824FFC24A39D708FCC03E41" box="[783,872,1123,1149]" pageId="26" pageNumber="27" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
, which is unique within 
<taxonomicName id="CFDE4D63B824FFC24D4BD708FA803E41" baseAuthorityName="Schaum" baseAuthorityYear="1862" box="[1149,1320,1123,1149]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Heptodonta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="26" pageNumber="27" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="melanopyga">
<emphasis id="3AAAEAF2B824FFC24D4BD708FA803E41" box="[1149,1320,1123,1149]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="27">H. melanopyga</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
